00:03:34.320 --> 00:03:35.320
[Amit Varma]: like.

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:41.080
[Amit Varma]: But 40 minutes with Steven Pinker is still 40 minutes of enlightenment now, who can complain

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:42.080
[Amit Varma]: about that?

